<div id="pf5a08" class="pf w7e h360" data-page-no="5a08"><div class="pc pc5a08 w7e h360"><div class="t m1126 x14 h24 y1db2 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From Homer A. Kent, </div><div class="t m1f2d x77 h3b y134 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Pastoral Epistles, </div><div class="t m875 x4f h24 y134 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 50. </div><div class="t m271 x26 h48 y2efa ff1 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction to 1 Timothy and Titus </div><div class="t m9d0 x61 h24 y2c2b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Our lessons this quarter are based on the letters of the apostle </div><div class="t m2fe x26 h24 y2b39 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paul to two young ministers and missionaries—Timothy and </div><div class="t ma49 x26 h24 y2a07 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Titus. Written against the backdrop of the first-century Chris-</div><div class="t m6f9 x26 h24 y2109 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tian church, these letters contain admonitions and guidelines </div><div class="t mb18 x26 h24 y2334 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that are timeless. They speak to </div><div class="t m267b x90 h3b y2334 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all </div><div class="t m4c4 x70 h24 y2334 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who carry responsibility in </div><div class="t md1b x26 h24 y20ef ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the church—every follower of Christ. Because we are a royal </div><div class="t m6e x26 h24 y853 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">priesthood (1 Peter 2:9), every believer is called to contribute to </div><div class="t mea4 x26 h24 yb74 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the life of the church and to fulfill Christ&apos;s mission in the world. </div><div class="t m48a xa4 h51 yeae ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE OF 1 TIMOTHY </div><div class="t m7d6 x60 h24 y3c0 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. </div><div class="t m1ea x65 h24 y3c0 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Salutation, 1:1, 2. </div><div class="t m477 x28 h24 y2ee ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. </div><div class="t m31a x83 h24 y730 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Charge to Rebuke False Teachers, 1:3-2